@node play "how do I play this game!"


Joystick 1 & 2:

         Up ......... Jump
         Left ....... Walk left
         Right ...... Walk right
         Fire ....... Punch
         Fire+Down .. Kick


Keyboard:

         F10 ........ Turbo Mode on/off
         P .......... Pause
         Esc ........ Return to title screen  (on title screen ... Quit)



@{"thats easy! " link main}

@endnode

